name: GU Campfire S'more Gel
description:
Smokey s’mores sweetness, no burnt fingers.  Get a tasty shot of carbohydrate blend (70-80% maltodextrin and 30-20% fructose). The mix is easy to digest and gives you a long-lasting surge of energy.Includes electrolytes to ensure hydration, antioxidants to stave off muscle tissue damage, and amino acids to delay muscle fatigue.Ingredients: maltodextrin, water, fructose, organic cocoa liquor, leucine, natural flavour, potassium citrate, sodium citrate, citric acid, calcium carbonate, sea salt, valine, isoleucine, gellan gum, sunflower oil, sodium benzoate (preservative), potassium sorbate (preservative).
